aces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買啲好少少嘅 牛腩都唔只廿蚊啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛腩一斤百幾蚊呀弱智，廿蚊整到咖哩腩真係笑鳩死我"},{"pid":"e778f71b2eb58020d86b9ad85ab21436f7b9e6c2","tid":236892,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:27:49.000Z","msg":"食太興已經戇鳩 重要食餐蛋飯 你老母生舊午餐肉好過"},{"pid":"48543c74b2f083fc173fb8f9563a255d50436eda","tid":236892,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n早十年前佢同美心d燒味飯係好味<br />\n宜家真係垃圾"},{"pid":"b4dbb8be5af73f85c191e74e6e182c90beb00dbe","tid":236892,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:38:19.000Z","msg":"食太興一向戇能鳩，又貴又唔好食"},{"pid":"2be2718e0f030a6b39b239c90c8456e42988b46e","tid":236892,"uid":1637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又係兩塊午餐肉，兩隻煎蛋，有乜問題呀</blockquote><br />\nD料係冇問題呀 價錢咪係問題囉 有錢仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪撚出街食啦，日日返屋企煮咪平囉<br />\n<br />\n叫完又屌鳩人貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家係屌太興貴呀，唔係出去食貴呀<br />\n幾時講過唔會出去食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大把地方平撚過太興啦 on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過明知太興係垃圾，樓豬都重要去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c824abefd3f0be0de3fde460ad4a0bd64f2c20","tid":236892,"uid":2337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9035aa7fdcd5c1aa868b075ffcfca6bf831c424e","tid":236892,"uid":9965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0